data.description: CORNER LOT! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath is ready for you to call home. Home has wonderful natural light, eat-in kitchen, formal living room and family room. Split floor plan and inside laundry. Yard is partially fenced. 2019 shingle ROOF, 2019 AC. Located in the fast growing area bordering Ocala just off SR 200. FIRST, LAST, SECURITY REQUIRED before move in. Pets ok. Owner must approve pets. Renter's liability insurance required with pet policy and proof of shot records.
